text: There is a dog run, though some areas in the dog run has plasticky/shattered glass debris. My pup had fun and didnt get any accidents so it was an awesome time!
A nice cosy place for basketball, walk the dog park and gathering with family.
Nice place to have peaceful time. Well maintained park, for students, adults who can have quality time to study, exercise. All those who stay near by can enjoy often visiting this place.

A lovely local neighbourhood park with a fine dose of greenery, sizeable playground, basketball court, dog run, amongst other amenities, with the general park layout showing an amazing tinge of European flavour... highly recommended
Great place for basketball and a sort of track around the basketball court, playground and workout station where you can run and there are measurements to complete a whole 400m
